			<TD VALIGN=top><BR><P><FONT FACE=Verdana,Arial,Helvetica,Helv,Monaco SIZE=-1><B>Illustration of Inner Circulation</B> (detail)<br>
<A HREF="javascript:launchHelp('/taoism/glossary/qing.php', 'width=250,height=275')">Qing dynasty</A>,<BR> 19th century<br>
